{"tid":2083618,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"西環集中營：《自治法》波及銀行 商界嚇到腳軟 - 季陶","createTime":"2020-06-29T01:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T01:26:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"142cffeaf3802b6c6701b27e50dc690242e313a2","tid":2083618,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/SP4JF2FFP5ZWMC7TTF7FXHFJIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FSP4JF2FFP5ZWMC7TTF7FXHFJIY%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Y%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=4269c7cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FSP4JF2FFP5ZWMC7TTF7FXHFJIY%2F&h=37fb7371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/SP4JF2FFP5ZWMC7TTF7FXHFJIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：《自治法》波及銀行 商界嚇到腳軟 - 季陶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xIgGmv4qJMeu1GVoeY7JoB0Hzr8=/640x508/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/62I7RSF6XLDKXOHLTXH4X335WY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxIgGmv4qJMeu1GVoeY7JoB0Hzr8%3D%2F640x508%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F62I7RSF6XLDKXOHLTXH4X335WY.jpg&h=67098b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《香港自治法案》容許美國制裁個人及機構，亦會波及與他們有往來的銀行，商界的鍾國斌早前形容法案「辣到冇得頂」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會本周二通過港版國安法並即時實施，恐怕並無懸念，美國政府早前公佈了針對性制裁措施，美國參議院更極速通過較《香港人權與民主法案》更辣的《香港自治法案》。有專業界中人直言，相對《香港人權與民主法案》，商界、金融界更擔心《香港自治法案》，因為有關法案容許美國行政機關更容易針對個人及機構作出制裁，亦會波及與他們有往來的銀行，「好多商界都希望美國政府只係擺吓姿態，如果嚟真用呢條法案（制裁），恐怕對香港商界打擊好大」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟動門檻低易中招<br />\n<br />\n該專業界人士指《香港自治法案》啟動門檻較民主人權法更低，「因為只要國務院認為邊啲人同機構令中國冇履行《中英聯合聲明》同《基本法》對港義務，就可以提出制裁，基本上想點郁都得」，更<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早前代表商界的自由黨黨魁鍾國斌形容有關法案「辣到冇得頂」，「<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n為了不想損害中美貿易利益，只是擺擺姿態，不會真的用這條法案制裁。<br />\n<br />\n季陶<br />\n周一、三、五刊出"},{"pid":"54896825db6704e77547ea4291d47e9881f23219","tid":2083618,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b313b4a7ac3085392f4337be181c918bb1b5431","tid":2083618,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"波叔話所謂制裁來的"},{"pid":"5015cd33ac9de0d091dd1b62fe16dd8256e95a7d","tid":2083618,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"劏房波話唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}